    <h4><b>About Us</b></h4>
    <p>We are the Future is the result of an idea shared and believed by volunteers from around the world who came together in an effort of cooperation for the sake of building a better planet. Every year, more and more people join our efforts to reforest and protect the forests and wildlife. Our foundation is already active in more than 50 countries and leads major projects in areas degraded by human activity.</p>
